you can replace pistons and cyl without spliting the case. depending on 
how long you want to keep the engine, your wallet, and the condition of 
the rest of the engine.

you can replace all of the cyl. and I have even swapped out a single cyl 
and piston when I was desperate and got 10,000 mile on it.

